        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Immunoelectron microscopy using the pre-embedding immunoperoxidase method detects CtBP2 immunoreactivity in the molecular layer of the cerebellum exclusively in presynaptic terminals of both asymmetric and symmetric synapses.. Experimental description: Brains of adult C57/BL6 mice of mixed sex were used in all biochemical experiments and for preparation of brain slices p.2." ;
